title: Cowboys-Giants MNF Preview, NFL Coaching Futures (Football 11/4)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Jared Dubin to preview Cowboys-Giants on Monday Night Football (1:05). Then, Will is joined by CBS Sports NFL Insider Jason La Canfora to break down the Browns' (29:45) and Jets' woes (43:00), Mike McCarthy's possible return to the league (50:30), as well as the quarterbacking futures of Cam Newton, Andy Dalton, Mitch Trubisky and Gardner Minshew.
